<HEADLINE> British Minister Visits UAE </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ABU DHABI, June 24 (Xinhua) - Derek Fatchett, Britain's
Minister of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs arrived
here today for a two-day visit as part of his Gulf tour.
</P>
<P>
During his visit, he is expected to meet UAE's senior
officials to discuss relations between the two countries and the
latest developments in the Middle East region.
</P>
<P>
