parties among the 12 called the National Patriotic Coalition.
</P>
<P>
Another 12 opposition parties called the Alliance of Opposition
Parties have also expressed their willingness to have talks with
the government. The United National Independence Party (UNIP) led
by former President Kenneth Kaunda is one members of the
alliance.  
