<HEADLINE> Chinese Premier Meets With Russian First Deputy Prime Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 25 (Xinhua) -- Premier Li Peng, meeting in
Beijing this afternoon with Russia's First Deputy Prime Minister
Boris Nemtsov, said he hopes that China and Russia can jointly
push forward the continuous development of bilateral
good-neighborly friendship.
</P>
<P>
In welcoming Nemtsov on his first visit to China, Li mentioned
the good talks he had with Vice-Premier Li Lanqing Tuesday and the
discussions of key cooperative projects of common concern and the
progress during the talks.
</P>
<P>
Li said that he is looking forward to meeting with Prime
Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin, and that he believes the meeting
will have exciting results.
</P>
<P>
Li said that China attaches great importance to its
good-neighborly friendship with Russia, and that he hopes their
border will be a friendly one.
</P>
<P>
Li noted that the Sino-Russian strategic and cooperative
partnership is substantial and that the major task the two sides
now face is concentrating on expanding the sphere of cooperation
and to implement the agreements reached by the two sides as a
basis of exploring new cooperative projects.
</P>
<P>
China and Russia have established a mechanism for regular
meetings by prime ministers, Li said, and the most important thing
now is to improve the sub-committees' work to let them prepare
fully.
</P>
<P>
Nemtsov said that China will soon resume the exercise of
sovereignty over Hong Kong, a historical event of international
significance and one worth celebrating.
</P>
<P>
He spoke highly of the development of Russian-Chinese
relations, and said that bilateral cooperation is developing in
various ways, but noted that the current bilateral trade volume is
no more than seven billion US dollars, which is not a match for
the two countries' status and potential.
</P>
<P>
He pointed out that Russia has a positive attitude towards
cooperation with China in petroleum, natural gas, nuclear energy
and hydropower, and hopes that cooperation can have good results.
</P>
<P>
Li said that there are very good prospects for Sino-Russian
cooperation, and that Nemtsov, as the new chairman of the
committee for regular meetings and the sub-committee on bilateral
economic and trade cooperation, will make his own contribution to
bilateral relations.  
</P>
