<HEADLINE> Interview: Jardine Matheson Shows Confidence in HK Future (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
He noted that it is important to keep Hong Kong competitive, it
is important to preserve the strong features of Hong Kong, to
preserve the rule of law, and to preserve Hong Kong as a
corrupt-free society.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, he added, a level playing field is very important for
foreign investors.
</P>
<P>
He acknowledged that Hong Kong's economy must be kept in good
competitive shape in trade, investment, tourism and many other
