<HEADLINE> Germany's Inflation Slightly Up in June </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, June 25 (Xinhua) -- The cost of living in western Germany
was up 0.2 percent in June compared with the May figure, the
preliminary data disclosed today by the Federal Statistics Office
in Wiesbaden shows.
</P>
<P>
