<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, June 24 (Xinhua) -- The International Monetary Fund
(IMF) announced today the approval of the second annual loan of 35
million U.S. dollars to Mozambique under the Enhanced Structural
Adjustment Facility (ESAF).
