style of work, strict discipline and adequate logistical support.
</P>
<P>
 "Xinhua Daily Telegraph"
</P>
<P>
-- The paper devoted three and a half pages to the reports on
activities held nationwide and a number of foreign countries by
overseas Chinese to greet the return of Hong Kong to the
motherland on July 1.
</P>
