temperatures as high as 35 degrees centigrade, put finishing
touches on a stage at Tian'anmen Square on which performances will
be held during the evening of June 30 to greet Hong Kong's return
of the motherland. The 1,200-square-meter stage is the largest of
its kind ever built on the square.
</P>
<P>
